# Markdown Rules guide

## Title 

All markdown files created will be fully capitalized with kebab case delimiting individual words in the title.

## Location

All markdown file will be place inside docs folder with an appropriate sub directory.

## Body 

All body of markdown will adhere to markdown linting rules specified as.

## Footer

All markdown files need to have this specific footer at the bottom of each file:

---

> Modern-Day Software Engineering < https://unnsse.io > © 2026

All new content or subsequent edits should always remain above this Footer (nothing comes below it).